nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant (Talking Book Publishers Inc. audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Force Heretic I: Remnant is the unabridged audio version of the Legends novel of the same name, by authors Sean Williams and Shane Dix. The audiobook was performed by Bob Askey and was released by Talking Book Publishers Inc. in 2006.
